ai’, and has been assumed by many scholars to be a byname of the apostle   Nathaniel .  <i>Talmai</i> is a Hebrew name, said to mean ‘abounding in furrows’ (Numbers 13:22)."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Bartholomew de Mortimer was born about 1145, in Attleborough, Norfolk, England as the son of Robert de Mortimer. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Lucia de Clifford. He died after 1195."},"et":{"about 1145–after 1195":"umbes 1145–pärast 1195","1137–1180":"1137–1180","1143–1177":"1143–1177","1145–1195":"1145–1195","1138–1195":"1138–1195","1170–Male":"1170–Surnud","1173–1240":"1173–1240","1105–Male":"1105–Surnud","about 1170":"umbes 1170","around or before 1173":"umbes enne 1173","1143":"1143","1240":"1240","1173":"1173","1195":"1195","1170":"1170","1180":"1180","Abt 1195":"umbes 1195","1105":"1105","1138":"1138","1137":"1137","1145":"1145","1177":"1177","after 1195":"pärast 1195","about 1145":"umbes 1145","Attleborough, Norfolk, England":"Attleborough, Norfolk, England","Wigmore, Herefordshire, England":"Wigmore, Herefordshire, England","Ludlow, Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1145–after 1195":"noin 1145–1195 jälkeen","1137–1180":"1137–1180","1143–1177":"1143–1177","1145–1195":"1145–1195","1138–1195":"1138–1195","1170–Male":"1170–Kuollut","1173–1240":"1173–1240","1105–Male":"1105–Kuollut","about 1170":"noin 1170","around or before 1173":"ennen vuotta noin 1173","1143":"1143","1240":"1240","1173":"1173","1195":"1195","1170":"1170","1180":"1180","Abt 1195":"noin 1195","1105":"1105","1138":"1138","1137":"1137","1145":"1145","1177":"1177","after 1195":"1195 jälkeen","about 1145":"noin 1145","Attleborough, Norfolk, England":"Attleborough, Norfolk, England","Wigmore, Herefordshire, England":"Wigmore, Herefordshire, England","Ludlow, Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshir